<lb n="0578b11" ed="T"/>阿娜<note n="0578014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03868;＝&CB00600;知解反八【宋】【元】，&CB00600;知解切八【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03868;＝&CB00600;知解反八【宋】【元】，＝&CB00600;知解切八【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578014"><lem wit="【大】">&CB03868;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&CB00600;知解反八</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">&CB00600;知解切八</rdg></app><note place="inline">八</note>俱娜&CB00600;<note place="inline">九</note><note n="0578015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（遮&CB00942;…反）十一字＝（摩賀娜&CB00600;十者&CB00942;者&CB00942;係麼澆）十二字【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（遮&CB00942;…反）十一字＝（摩賀娜&CB00600;十者&CB00942;者&CB00942;係麼澆）十二字【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app word-count="11" n="0578015"><lem wit="【大】">遮&CB00942;遮&CB00942;<note place="inline">十</note>係麼澆<note place="inline">牛矯反</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">摩賀娜&CB00600;十者&CB00942;者&CB00942;係麼澆</rdg></app>
