<lb n="0578b15" ed="T"/>犁<note place="inline">二十一</note>彌者犁<note place="inline">二十二</note>麼尾<note n="0578021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">覽＝&CB00772;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">覽＝&CB00772;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578021"><lem wit="【大】">覽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&CB00772;</rdg></app>麼<note place="inline">二十三</note>戶<note n="0578022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">毛＝&CB02802;【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毛＝&CB02802;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578022"><lem wit="【大】">毛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&CB02802;</rdg></app>戶
<lb n="0578b16" ed="T"/><app source="0578022" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">毛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&CB02802;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二十四</note>唵<note n="0578023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二十五麼折囉＝&CB00085;曰囉二合【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二十五麼折囉＝&CB00085;曰囉二合【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578023"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二十五</note>麼折囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&CB00085;曰囉二合</rdg></app>諭<note n="0578024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">師＝曬【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">師＝曬【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578024"><lem wit="【大】">師</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">曬</rdg></app><note place="inline">某甲<note n="0578025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二十六〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔二十六〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578025"><lem wit="【大】">二十六</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0578b17" ed="T"/><note n="0578026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＝二合賀引二十五【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶＝二合賀引二十五【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578026"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">二合賀引二十五</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578b1801">爾時十方佛所。一切執金剛菩薩異口同音
<lb n="0578b19" ed="T"/>亦說延命陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0578b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578b2001" type="dharani">吽<note n="0578027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578027" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>〔引〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578027"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>吽<note place="inline">引</note>尸棄薩&CB00085;<note place="inline"><note n="0578028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二合引＝引二合【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合引＝引二合【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578028"><lem wit="【大】">二合引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">引二合</rdg></app></note><note n="0578029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶引＝賀一引【宋】，賀引【元】，賀引一【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶引＝賀一引【宋】，＝賀引【元】，＝賀引一【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578029"><lem wit="【大】">訶<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">賀一引</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">賀引</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">賀引一</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578b2101">如是一切如來及十方執金剛菩薩。說是陀
<lb n="0578b22" ed="T"/>羅尼已隱而不現。</p>
<lb n="0578b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578b2301">爾時毘沙門天王白佛言。我<note n="0578030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔亦〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔亦〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578030"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>以佛神力。為
<lb n="0578b24" ed="T"/>一切眾生加持護念。除非命故說陀羅<note n="0578031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尼＋（曰）【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼＋（曰）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578031"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0578b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578b2501" type="dharani">始尾<note place="inline">二合<note n="0578032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔下同〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔下同〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578032"><lem wit="【大】">下同</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>帝<note place="inline">一</note>始<note n="0578033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尾＋（二合）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尾＋（二合）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578033"><lem wit="【大】">尾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尾<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>怛犁<note place="inline">二</note>栗<note n="0578034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＋（三）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利＋（三）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578034"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">利<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578b2601">爾時毘樓勒叉天王又白佛言。我<app source="0578030" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>以佛神
<lb n="0578b27" ed="T"/><note n="0578035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">力＋（故）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">力＋（故）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578035"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">力故</rdg></app>。為多眾生除夭命故。說陀<note n="0578036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉＝羅【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578036"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">羅</rdg></app><app source="0578031" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0578b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578b2801" type="dharani">摩<note n="0578037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">登＝蹬【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">登＝蹬【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578037"><lem wit="【大】">登</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">蹬</rdg></app>霓<note n="0578038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578038"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>摩<note n="0578039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">登儗尼二＝蹬倪尼一【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">登儗尼二＝蹬倪尼一【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578039"><lem wit="【大】">登儗尼<note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">蹬倪尼一</rdg></app>輸<note n="0578040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麼輸麼＝摩輸【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼輸麼＝摩輸【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578040"><lem wit="【大】">麼輸麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">摩輸</rdg></app>謀<note place="inline"><note n="0578041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三＝二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578041"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0578b29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578b2901">爾時提頭賴吒天王亦白佛言。我亦為諸眾
<pb n="0578c" id="T20.1135.0578c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0578c01" ed="T"/>生。除死怖故說陀羅<app source="0578031" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0578c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578c0201" type="dharani">者&CB01238;者&CB01238;<note place="inline">一</note>者囉<note n="0578042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02740;＝哩引二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02740;＝哩引二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578042"><lem wit="【大】">&CB02740;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">哩引二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578c0301">爾時毘樓博叉天王亦白佛言。我亦以佛神
<lb n="0578c04" ed="T"/>力故。令一切眾生除非命故說陀羅<app source="0578031" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0578c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578c0501" type="dharani">未臨<note place="inline">一</note><note n="0578043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麼麼麼＝&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼麼麼＝&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578043"><lem wit="【大】">麼麼麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0578c0601">佛告四天王言。若有讀誦此經。日日受持乃
<lb n="0578c07" ed="T"/>至一遍。<note n="0578044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當＋（應）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＋（應）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578044"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">當應</rdg></app>敬彼善男子善女人。應如佛想終
<lb n="0578c08" ed="T"/>不墮三惡道定增壽命。若人每日。為一切眾
<lb n="0578c09" ed="T"/>生轉<note n="0578045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">讀＝誦【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">讀＝誦【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578045"><lem wit="【大】">讀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">誦</rdg></app>此經。終無夭死短命之怖。亦無惡夢
<lb n="0578c10" ed="T"/>魘魅&CB00057;。<note n="0578046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">咀＝詛【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咀＝詛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578046"><lem wit="【大】">咀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">詛</rdg></app>惡形羅剎鬼神之怖。亦不為水火
<lb n="0578c11" ed="T"/>兵毒之所傷害。一切諸佛菩薩攝受護念其
<lb n="0578c12" ed="T"/>處。亦為佛所護持。爾時世尊說是經已。毘沙
<lb n="0578c13" ed="T"/>門天王等一切大眾。皆大歡喜信受奉行。</p>
<lb n="0578c14" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0578047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0578047"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&lac;</rdg></app>一切如來金剛壽命陀羅尼經<note n="0578048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本奧書曰貞享三年九月十七日點校了淨嚴四十八載，元祿十六年正月二十九日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note></jhead></juan></div1>
